{"tid":1307744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議大家唔好死守連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:33:32.000Z","uid":2300,"like":123,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"132237cf59437aa5af5b73b83d3bcdf0b69d470e","tid":1307744,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"班藍絲開始搞連儂牆，輿論同視線開始比人轉移<br />\n其實都係意料之中 全部都只係政府既一貫玩法&hellip;<br />\n連儂牆 ＞ 兩派衝突 ，等你地自己人打自己人 ＞  消耗民氣<br />\n<br />\n認真&hellip;玩多一兩日好啦 <br />\n記住！你守嬴連儂牆又點？守嬴d memo唔會有真普選，對五大訴求都只會係零作用&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n死守係無意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家班藍絲 ／ 死警犬／休班警實係打遊擊，得閒落黎挑釁班學生&hellip;大家再為連儂牆死鬥，最後嬴家只會係政府<br />\n<br />\n希望大家識得放手，目標清晰地繼續向前行&hellip;比人拆可以由佢，最緊要唔好中計同唔好受傷"},{"pid":"b4bc69ccbab64675acd53b379fc7b4cf0b7aa4c6","tid":1307744,"uid":2300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"大家真係要向前走，唔好比牆封死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78638af885e785610103ba8914a633ff6be6942","tid":1307744,"uid":53870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"31d1a8660fbbdf3091f73f7130e489d3c8cb3611","tid":1307744,"uid":2300,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"大家要進化，玩長輩圖打文宣輿論戰＞＞＞死守儂牆"},{"pid":"da818105cc9213130b24a8f4c846e5abbe9a8b7b","tid":1307744,"uid":270824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:41:50.000Z","msg":"推！重要！七大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307734</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9fdbdd49b27e8f89484fe8a20694492e5212e1","tid":1307744,"uid":2300,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:44:56.000Z","msg":"希望各巴絲唔好太集中連儂牆<br />\n我知每一張memo都係有心人貼上去，比藍絲破壞你會覺得好唔開心想去守&hellip;但真係要識得放手"},{"pid":"9c66bd